// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0632 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 12b11cf3-a1da-519b-adc2-506db0373038

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*amazonlinux:2023*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:7*" or process.executable like~ "*oraclelinux:8*" or process.executable like~ "*redhat/ubi9:*")
